  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222250/extras/cfad479f8a82f2323437fe88dc9bc362.poster.avif?t=1745608594\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222250/extras/cfad479f8a82f2323437fe88dc9bc362.webm?t=1745608594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222250/extras/cfad479f8a82f2323437fe88dc9bc362.mp4?t=1745608594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Mini Knight's Journey is a linear action-adventure platformer game about two twin brothers who, with their father, go on a journey to defeat the school bullies!<br><br><strong>Freatures:</strong><br><br>• 2 Playable Characters! Play with Mini Knight, the Brave, or Mini Bond, the Stylish, each one in your journey!<br><br>• Elemental Magics! Use powers against enemies and access hidden passages!<br><br>• 5 Thematic Worlds! Travel with your father around the city of Brave Harbor!<br> <br>• Progression System! Defeat enemies or collect stars to gain levels and unlock upgrades!<br><br>• Classic Mode! A extra challenge to the skillful!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222250/extras/0415388bffba36a88232fe6c33f3d697.poster.avif?t=1745608594\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222250/extras/0415388bffba36a88232fe6c33f3d697.webm?t=1745608594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222250/extras/0415388bffba36a88232fe6c33f3d697.mp4?t=1745608594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222250/extras/c1fef2566835cc7f8734f26de619bb2d.poster.avif?t=1745608594\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222250/extras/c1fef2566835cc7f8734f26de619bb2d.webm?t=1745608594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222250/extras/c1fef2566835cc7f8734f26de619bb2d.mp4?t=1745608594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
